--> Proactive Nudges: Agents should identify needs before users articulate them—suggesting actions, drafting content, or identifying potential issues—without being intrusive.
--> Multimodal Inputs: Allow users to switch seamlessly between voice, text, and visual inputs (e.g., uploading a sketch) based on their context.


















